Mister Machine: Death Star

Boilerplate theme for rapid WordPress theme development. Featured include:

# HTML5 Boilerplate integration
# Responsive CSS
# Inclusion of common JavaScript libraries: Modernizr, jQuery UI (tabs, dialog and datepicker), and jQuery Validation
# Asynchronous Social Widget Scripts for Facebook, Twitter, Google+
# MailChimp API class
# Capistrano Deployment script


To Use:

# Set your environment configuration in wp-config.php. Don't forget to get a new set of Authentication Unique Keys and Salts and adjust your table_prefix as needed.
# Add an environment trigger file one directory above your project: "env_local", "env_test", etc.
# For Capistrano deployment, add your deployment settings to /config/deploy.rb
